{"tid":969142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"石排灣邨貓咪墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-01-04T19:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T02:47:37.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e15fe0b62d54615821f1261a574b6b4e7899a0f","tid":969142,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T19:53:35.000Z","msg":"香港仔石排灣邨碧園樓，凌晨零時許，有街坊在大廈對開公園閒聊，其間聽到巨響，發現一隻花貓倒臥地上，疑從高處墮下。警方接報到場，證實貓隻已死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方未能聯絡貓主，召愛護動物協會人員將貓屍撿走。據稱，墮樓貓隻是成年貓女，愛協初步調查死因無可疑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190105/59106867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190105%2F59106867&d=DbxBOx%2F23dnJ1bxTII96To9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2c747b55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190105%2F59106867&h=abb90ad3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190105/59106867</a>"},{"pid":"208cc6e25b920b64ec0fa98d44cdc040cd3029f9","tid":969142,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T19:59:05.000Z","msg":"飛天貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987db35c3249129e698e1e5bf836e27c5033fd90","tid":969142,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T19:59:23.000Z","msg":"裝窗網啦冚家鏟"},{"pid":"7caf29b0c68b5cbe5042a80d49532462a6498e78","tid":969142,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T21:53:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"428dd2d179ee3a417ecfc950da62f4b268988094","tid":969142,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T22:01:54.000Z","msg":"冇新聞呀？"},{"pid":"6e98336b07c9a6bfd7aa708ccc17f1de9bdd22bf","tid":969142,"uid":43041,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T22:12:17.000Z","msg":"香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線 : 23892222<br />\n<b